            "text": "Very nice apartment, just in \"Mitte\" and very close to Naturkundemuseum with a great Dinosaurs collection!! a must see!\nIf coming by car, take care of road construction and detours.",
            "picture": "https://a2.muscache.com/ic/users/9335616/profile_pic/1381391371/original.jpg?interpolation=lanczos-none&crop=w:w;*,*&crop=h:h;*,*&resize=225:*&output-format=jpg&output-quality=70",
